   Once upon a time , in a forest , there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree , which was  on the banks  on the river. In the same
    forest , there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day , the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.
     the kind hearted monkey  offered him some fruits. the nest day, the crocodile came back for more fruits as he loved them. As days passed by
     , the crocodile and the monkey became good friends.